，通過出售固網電訊，交易作價145億元，買方為投資管理公司I Squared Capital。集團主席霍建寧表示，動議獲全數在場股東通過。被問到交易後會否派發特別息，或利用資金作發展收購，霍建寧表示，需留待今年12月董事會商討資金用途，「(集團)都未收到錢」。<br />\n<br />\n和記電訊股價今日高開，報2.93元，一度升至2.95元，期後回落至2.92水平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1504770631419&amp;issue=20170907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1504770631419%26issue%3D20170907&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=4e33131c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1504770631419&amp;issue=20170907</a>"},{"pid":"5c5b88934b506535b27199fef80215a5d717f855","tid":1000132,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef4e351d0ebf0093d0843616ff6c1e8a71232ac9","tid":1000132,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:03:56.000Z","msg":"霍生走數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之前已經放晒<br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2017年9月7日 15:40<br />\n【憧憬特別息】和記電訊：留待12月董事會商討派發特別息<br />\n<br />\n和記電訊（0215） 今日舉行臨時股東大會，通過出售固網電訊，交易作價145億元，買方為投資管理公司I Squared Capital。集團主席霍建寧表示，動議獲全數在場股東通過。被問到交易後會否派發特別息，或利用資金作發展收購，霍建寧表示，需留待今年12月董事會商討資金用途，「(集團)都未收到錢」。<br />\n<br />\n和記電訊股價今日高開，報2.93元，一度升至2.95元，期後回落至2.92水平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1504770631419&amp;issue=20170907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1504770631419%26issue%3D20170907&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=4e33131c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1504770631419&amp;issue=20170907</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:07:59.000Z","msg":"已經持有一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e141c628806c16db8d9da53e2a52d3a6a27d7ec5","tid":1000132,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"351c0e07c4ee03ce047316c0fba747883c0607ed","tid":1000132,"ui